## Architecture Decision Log

| Date | Decision | Reasoning |
|---|---|---|
| Mar 2, 2026 | VPS over OBS-always-on for 24/7 radio | Stream survives laptop downtime. Critical for Athens move. $6/mo. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | 6fps animation speed | 24fps too fast, 12fps still too fast. 6fps matches lofi ambient feel. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | Restream Standard over Free | Free plan has visible branding watermark. Standard removes it + supports 3 channels. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | Deferred seamless handoff (nginx-rtmp) | VPS live and working. Brief blip acceptable. Revisit when streams are regular. |
| Mar 2026 | Mac Mini M4 chosen over Windows mini PC | macOS no forced restarts. VideoToolbox hardware encode. Silent. $22/year electricity. |
| Mar 2026 | Warmup/cooldown revised to 28:07 | 70:07 too long. 28:00 = 1680 seconds (divisible by 7). 28:07 carries septimal DNA visibly. |
| Mar 2026 | LoFi Radio moves to @the_outside_inn | @EIWerner = scheduled streams, VODs, public content. Outside Inn = ambient community layer. |

